President Donald Trump has announced his intention to nominate a new wave of judicial nominees. The nominees include Greg G. Guidry, who will serve as District Judge on the U.S. District Court for the Eastern District of Louisiana. James Wesley Hendrix has been nominated as District Judge on the U.S. District Court for the Northern District of Texas. Sean D. Jordan has been nominated as District Judge on the U.S. District Court for the Eastern District of Texas. Michael T. Liburdi has been nominated as District Judge on the U.S. District Court for the District of Arizona. Lastly, Mark T. Pittman has been nominated as District Judge on the U.S. District Court for the Northern District of Texas. Peter D. Welte has been nominated as District Judge on the U.S. District Court for the District of North Dakota.